00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:39,540
There is even worse.

276
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:42,260
One year, the dean talked
to him about it,

277
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:43,820
and he said,

278
00:20:43,888 --> 00:20:45,420
"How dare you treat me like this?

279
00:20:45,420 --> 00:20:46,860
I'll make the course even harder."

280
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:48,380
And he did.

281
00:20:48,700 --> 00:20:49,933
How hard are we talking?

282
00:20:50,006 --> 00:20:52,140
The passing rate dropped to 10%.

283
00:20:54,340 --> 00:20:56,780
That's a real nightmare.

284
00:20:56,980 --> 00:20:57,780
I can't believe

285
00:20:58,220 --> 00:20:59,640
people still bring up

286
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:01,180
ancient history like that.

287
00:21:07,340 --> 00:21:08,020
Professor Wang,

288
00:21:08,580 --> 00:21:11,466
she's a first-year psych student
who is at the bottom of the class.

289
00:21:11,533 --> 00:21:13,844
- Professor Wang, hello.
- Professor Wang, hello.

290
00:21:14,220 --> 00:21:16,311
Professor Wang, thank you
for explaining it to me.

291
00:21:16,540 --> 00:21:18,340
I don't have any more questions.

292
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:21,100
Stop right there.

293
00:21:24,820 --> 00:21:28,060
About what you said earlier,
that data is wrong.

294
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:30,540
The passing rate wasn't 10%.

295
00:21:30,620 --> 00:21:31,820
It was 5%.

296
00:21:32,111 --> 00:21:33,666
There were 61 students in the class.

297
00:21:33,733 --> 00:21:35,380
Only three students passed.

298
00:21:43,380 --> 00:21:45,780
Jian Dan, he is terrifying.

299
00:21:45,826 --> 00:21:47,460
Do you still want to take Applied Math?

300
00:21:48,060 --> 00:21:49,820
Well, there is still a 5% chance
of passing.

301
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:51,540
You're seriously amazing.

302
00:21:51,933 --> 00:21:53,780
I can't help but admire you.

303
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:57,900
I am doomed.

304
00:21:58,580 --> 00:22:00,120
(Your final grades now depend
more on club involvement.)

305
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:00,929
What's it?

306
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:02,500
To get students more involved

307
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:03,780
in club activities,

308
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:05,460
the university increases

309
00:22:05,820 --> 00:22:07,700
club involvement in final grades.

310
00:22:07,822 --> 00:22:10,377
What are you going to do
about your club activities now?

311
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:12,180
Won't it affect your scholarship?

312
00:22:14,180 --> 00:22:16,486
Do you think
Han Yansheng will kick me out

313
00:22:16,580 --> 00:22:18,260
if I go back to the Swimming Club?

314
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:19,220
He won't.

315
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:21,620
Because he would never let you back in.

316
00:22:23,700 --> 00:22:25,460
I was messing with you.

317
00:22:25,866 --> 00:22:27,333
If the Swimming Club doesn't want you,

318
00:22:27,333 --> 00:22:29,240
you can join another one.

319
00:22:29,900 --> 00:22:32,186
The recruitment is over.

320
00:22:32,286 --> 00:22:34,033
No club is accepting new members now.

321
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:35,773
Yes, regular clubs don't accept

322
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:37,500
new members now.

323
00:22:37,540 --> 00:22:39,260
What if it's a new club?

324
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:41,540
Check the school forum later.

325
00:22:41,700 --> 00:22:44,177
Maybe you'll get lucky.

326
00:22:46,820 --> 00:22:48,526
Starting a new club?

327
00:22:49,220 --> 00:22:50,380
Our Cosplay Club

328
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:52,420
was only formed last semester.

329
00:22:58,660 --> 00:22:59,900
What are you thinking?

330
00:23:09,260 --> 00:23:10,060
Sorry,

331
00:23:10,333 --> 00:23:12,380
your application
to start the Rock Climbing Club

332
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:13,660
has been rejected.

333
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:16,340
That area is currently managed
by the Swimming Club.

334
00:23:16,460 --> 00:23:18,733
You will need authorization

335
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:20,340
from the club president, Han Yansheng.

336
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:31,177
Am I supposed to go plead with him now?

337
00:23:41,340 --> 00:23:42,100
Han Yansheng!

338
00:23:44,155 --> 00:23:45,380
This is a training facility.

339
00:23:45,460 --> 00:23:46,860
No unauthorized entry.

340
00:23:48,066 --> 00:23:50,177
(Club Authorization Application)
I need to talk to you.

341
00:23:50,340 --> 00:23:51,900
I have class. No time.

342
00:23:54,580 --> 00:23:55,260
Monkey.

343
00:23:57,300 --> 00:23:58,340
Hey, Jian Dan.

344
00:23:58,740 --> 00:23:59,140
But I...

345
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:06,180
That's what Han is like.

346
00:24:06,460 --> 00:24:07,740
Don't take it personally.

347
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:14,660
I'm off to my elective class.

348
00:24:19,380 --> 00:24:20,380
Why is it always me?

349
00:24:23,460 --> 00:24:24,180
Han Yansheng.

350
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:26,580
Here's your book back.

351
00:24:26,820 --> 00:24:27,420
Thanks.

352
00:24:37,580 --> 00:24:38,760
Why are you following me?

353
00:24:39,900 --> 00:24:40,580
I'm not.

354
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:41,740
I have class here.

355
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:44,140
What do you want?

356
00:24:44,822 --> 00:24:46,888
(Club Authorization Application)
Please sign this

357
00:24:46,911 --> 00:24:49,377
and return the second-floor space
to the Rock Climbing Club.

358
00:24:51,111 --> 00:24:52,540
The Rock Climbing Club was disbanded.

359
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:54,620
Exactly.

360
00:24:54,940 --> 00:24:56,420
But the moment you sign this,

361
00:24:56,700 --> 00:24:58,380
we can revive it.

362
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:02,100
Wait, you're starting
a Rock Climbing Club?

363
00:25:02,977 --> 00:25:04,260
All that's missing is the venue.

364
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:06,060
Stop wasting your time.

365
00:25:06,860 --> 00:25:07,540
I'm not signing.

366
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:13,460
That space originally belonged

367
00:25:13,540 --> 00:25:14,900
to the Rock Climbing Club.

368
00:25:15,100 --> 00:25:16,940
The pool
was just managing it temporarily.

369
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:19,020
Now, we're reviving the club.

370
00:25:19,420 --> 00:25:20,700
It's only fair to return it.

371
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:21,660
Why won't you sign?

372
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:22,955
Since I'm managing it now,

373
00:25:23,100 --> 00:25:24,940
I get to decide who uses it.

374
00:25:24,980 --> 00:25:25,660
And

375
00:25:26,260 --> 00:25:27,380
you're not on my list.

376
00:25:28,380 --> 00:25:29,700
This is personal, isn't it?

377
00:25:29,866 --> 00:25:31,022
I don't care what you think.

378
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:36,940
Then what do I have to do

379
00:25:36,940 --> 00:25:38,220
to get your signature?

380
00:25:38,355 --> 00:25:39,288
The class is starting.

381
00:25:43,066 --> 00:25:45,888
(Chapter One: The Limit)

382
00:25:52,460 --> 00:25:54,060
That's all for today's lecture.

383
00:25:54,660 --> 00:25:55,660
Here's my email.

384
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:58,820
If you have any questions,

385
00:25:59,300 --> 00:26:00,500
feel free to reach out.

386
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:06,140
Now, can we talk?

387
00:26:07,180 --> 00:26:07,940
Please excuse me.

388
00:26:09,444 --> 00:26:10,688
The authorization form.

389
00:26:12,740 --> 00:26:13,380
Let me see.

390
00:26:29,672 --> 00:26:31,380
(Club Authorization Application)

391
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:54,980
Han.

392
00:26:55,340 --> 00:26:56,900
Han, you're finally here.

393
00:26:56,900 --> 00:26:58,060
Shi has been wearing me out.

394
00:26:58,688 --> 00:27:00,480
You've been planning this
for a while, huh?

395
00:27:00,488 --> 00:27:01,300
Isn't it obvious?

396
00:27:01,300 --> 00:27:03,540
Shi always puts in effort
when it comes to Entong.

397
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:05,355
You'll have to wait a little longer.

398
00:27:05,377 --> 00:27:06,190
Entong is on her way.

399
00:27:15,820 --> 00:27:16,460
She's here.

400
00:27:33,140 --> 00:27:35,340
Long time no see, guys.

401
00:27:35,533 --> 00:27:36,355
It's been a while.

402
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:38,140
Look at her.

403
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:39,300
Still as gorgeous as ever.

404
00:27:39,860 --> 00:27:40,673
Welcome back.

405
00:27:41,340 --> 00:27:41,940
Thank you.

406
00:27:42,313 --> 00:27:43,906
I missed you guys so much

407
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:44,913
while I was on exchange.

408
00:27:50,206 --> 00:27:51,446
It looks like all this

409
00:27:51,620 --> 00:27:53,340
is for me, huh?

410
00:27:53,900 --> 00:27:55,780
Shi handled it all.

411
00:27:55,860 --> 00:27:57,380
We wouldn't dare take credit.

412
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:02,100
Shi, thanks.

413
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:04,100
I'm glad you like it.

414
00:28:05,146 --> 00:28:05,780
Oh,

415
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:07,340
I've prepared this for you too.

416
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:08,454
(Ocean University Life Guide)

417
00:28:08,540 --> 00:28:10,420
"Ocean University Life Guide?"

418
00:28:11,100 --> 00:28:13,726
I've only been gone a year.
It's not necessary.

419
00:28:14,066 --> 00:28:16,060
A lot has changed
at Ocean University in a year.

420
00:28:16,300 --> 00:28:17,380
There is a new cafeteria,

421
00:28:17,733 --> 00:28:19,380
and the piano rooms have moved.

422
00:28:20,860 --> 00:28:22,060
Then I have to check this out.

423
00:28:26,260 --> 00:28:28,300
Pasta is on the new cafeteria's
third floor.

424
00:28:28,540 --> 00:28:30,300
Sushi is on the second floor
of the old one.

425
00:28:30,666 --> 00:28:32,888
Milk tea is on the 1st floor
of the new cafeteria.

426
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:34,820
These are all my favorites.

427
00:28:36,493 --> 00:28:38,753
And the new piano room

428
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:40,460
is in Room 203 of the music building.

429
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,780
This is exactly what I need.

430
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:45,340
Shi, you're so thoughtful.

431
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:46,700
Glad you like it.

432
00:28:47,020 --> 00:28:47,900
I love it.

433
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:52,420
I don't see Yuan Sen around.

434
00:28:52,580 --> 00:28:53,260
Where is he?

435
00:28:53,733 --> 00:28:55,044
He stepped out for something.

436
00:28:56,060 --> 00:28:57,860
All right. Tell me.

437
00:28:58,020 --> 00:28:59,260
How has everyone been

438
00:28:59,260 --> 00:29:00,340
while I was gone?

439
00:29:00,466 --> 00:29:01,700
Same old.

440
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:03,540
But lately, we've met

441
00:29:03,540 --> 00:29:04,860
someone pretty interesting.

442
00:29:05,820 --> 00:29:06,533
Oh? Who?

443
00:29:06,980 --> 00:29:09,066
Just someone totally irrelevant.

444
00:29:09,220 --> 00:29:10,244
Han Yansheng!

445
00:29:40,778 --> 00:29:44,228
♪Suddenly the street view feels familiar♪

446
00:29:44,968 --> 00:29:48,438
♪Memories come too abruptly♪

447
00:29:49,908 --> 00:29:53,288
♪It feels nothing,
yet they come back time after time♪

448
00:29:54,178 --> 00:29:57,498
♪Where should I begin♪

449
00:29:58,248 --> 00:30:01,738
♪To reach back to that time?♪

450
00:30:03,088 --> 00:30:06,148
♪A certain look, a certain lyric♪

451
00:30:06,478 --> 00:30:12,188
♪Before I even start reminiscing,
my eyes are already wet♪

452
00:30:13,288 --> 00:30:17,068
♪It feels like a lifetime ago♪

453
00:30:17,438 --> 00:30:21,198
♪Those youthful little things♪

454
00:30:21,198 --> 00:30:24,148
♪Ordinary, yet meaningful♪

455
00:30:24,458 --> 00:30:30,108
♪Quietly speeding
through the cracks of time♪

456
00:30:30,778 --> 00:30:34,448
♪Those scattered past memories♪

457
00:30:34,938 --> 00:30:37,208
♪Names now blurred♪

458
00:30:37,468 --> 00:30:45,098
♪Thankfully, we once had each other♪

459
00:30:47,438 --> 00:30:51,068
♪Those youthful little things♪

460
00:30:51,068 --> 00:30:54,248
♪Heartbeats that needed no disguise♪

461
00:30:54,558 --> 00:31:00,188
♪When someday, promises became a luxury♪

462
00:31:00,758 --> 00:31:04,278
♪Those scattered past memories♪

463
00:31:04,538 --> 00:31:07,258
♪Were never truly lost♪

464
00:31:07,438 --> 00:31:15,088
♪They form the complete blueprint
of a colorful life♪
